                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8751" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1342</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2195 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双鸟在手难兼顾，不若一鸟归林去——江苏国泰分拆瑞泰新材上市之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Meeting the Growing Needs of Two Birds in Home is Difficult, So It&#39;s Better to Release One of Them Back into the Forest——the Process of GTIG Spin-off RTXC Listing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">常媛，萧慧娴，李瑞玲，廖伊，曾祁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏瑞泰新能源材料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏国泰；分拆上市；业务差异型分拆；市场选择</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">GTIG; Spin-off; Business-differentiated spin-off; Market selection</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">出于分散经营风险、拓展市场势力等目的，企业发展到一定规模后会进行一系列跨产品或跨行业的扩张性经营活动，培育差异性业务。随着各业务发展壮大，负协同效应逐渐凸显，企业经营压力和管理难度增加，如何促进各业务协同发展成为困扰诸多企业的问题。2019年《上市公司分拆所属子公司境内上市试点若干规定》、2022年《上市公司分拆规则（试行）》等新规陆续出台，分拆上市政策逐步完善，为解决这一难题提供了可行方案，A股市场也掀起分拆上市热潮。本案例以“供应链服务+化工新能源”双主业结构的江苏国泰分拆瑞泰新材上市为例，引导学生分析其分拆上市动因以及上市时机、板块选择的特点，并探究分拆上市后的效果，旨在加强学生对业务差异型分拆上市的思考，提升学生进行分拆上市相关决策的能力。最后，基于江苏国泰分拆瑞泰新材上市历程，给其他拟分拆差异性业务上市企业得出相关启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">For the purpose of diversifying business risks and expanding market power, enterprises will carry out a series of cross-product or cross-industry expansion business activities after developing to a certain scale to cultivate differentiated businesses. With the development and growth of each business, the negative synergy effect has gradually become prominent, and the operating pressure and management difficulty of enterprises have increased. How to promote the coordinated development of each business has become a problem plaguing many enterprises. New regulations such as the &quot;Several Regulations on the Domestic Listing Pilot of Listed Companies&#39; spin-off Subsidiaries&quot; in 2019 and the &quot;spin-off Rules for Listed Companies (Trial)&quot; in 2022 have been introduced successively, and the spin-off listing policy has gradually improved, providing A feasible solution to solve this problem, and the A-share market has also set off a spin-off listing boom. This case takes GTIG, which is engaged in both supply chain business and chemical new energy business, spun off RTXC for listing as an example to guide students to analyze the motivation for their spin-off and listing, as well the particular features of its choice of timing and segments for the listing, and examine the effects after the spin-off and listing. The aim is to strengthen students&#39; thinking about business-differentiated spin-offs and enhance their ability to make spin-off-related decisions. Finally, based on the listing process of GTIG&#39;s spin-off of RTXC, relevant enlightenment is drawn for other listed companies planning to spin-off different businesses.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《资本市场与上市筹划》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务差异型分拆上市模式；分拆上市动因；市场选择；市场时机理论；分拆上市后效果评价；价值管理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
